'    Traceback (most recent call last)' Text
':'           Text
'\n'          Text.Whitespace

'      File ' Text
'``'          Literal.String
"t.py'', line 15, in ?\n        print it.next()\n    StopIteration\n\nBecause " Literal.String
'`'           Literal.String
'`'           Literal.String
'yield'       Literal.String
'``'          Literal.String
' will often be returning ' Text
