'``'          Literal.String
' returns an infinite stream of' Text
'\n'          Text.Whitespace

'integers, increasing by 1 each time.  You can optionally supply the' Text
'\n'          Text.Whitespace

'starting number, which defaults to 0' Text
'::'          Literal.String.Escape
'\n\n'        Text

